summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting overhead underground distribution easements over portions of Vacated West Raye Street; Vacated Evanston Avenue North; Tract 6, Interurban Five Acre Gardens; Government Lot 2, Section 35, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M., Lot 12, Block 5, Irvington on the Sound; Lot "A" City of Lake Forest Park Short Subdivision No. SP-85-35; Parcel "C" and "D", City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 78-169; Vacated North 180th Street; Lot 17 and 18, Block 1, Stimson Park, Division No. 1; Lots 4 and 5, Block 9 University Lake Shore Addition, Divisions 1, 2 and 3, and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
